metadata.name: Balloon
metadata.description:
Balloon by ChatGPT

The US took aim and shot with might,  
A balloon in its sight.  
The skies grew still, the winds grew calm,  
As the object of destruction met its harm.

Tensions rose, the world took note,  
Of this event that stirred such hope.  
Why was the balloon brought down to earth?  
Only time will reveal its worth.

RIP
